       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. OPENCDML.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
016500         MOVE 'DC-CTRL-AREA' TO ROLLBACK-AREA-NAME
            OPEN DCCF-AREA-NAME USAGE-MODE IS RETRIEVAL 
            , DCCF-AREA-NAME2 USAGE-MODE IS UPDATE
            , DCCF-AREA-NAME3 USAGE-MODE IS RETRIEVAL
            , DCCF-AREA-NAME4 USAGE-MODE IS INITIAL LOAD
            , DCCF-AREA-NAME5 USAGE-MODE IS EXCLUSIVE RETRIEVAL
            , DCCF-AREA-NAME6 USAGE-MODE IS EXCLUSIVE UPDATE 
            
            OPEN ALL USAGE-MODE IS RETRIEVAL 
            
            OPEN DCCF-AREA-NAME USAGE-MODE IS PROTECTED RETRIEVAL 
            , DCCF-AREA-NAME2 USAGE-MODE IS UPDATE
            ON ERROR GO TO ENDLABEL
            
       ENDLABEL.
           GOBACK.
